oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Delivering milk
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of unidentified laborers about to load milk cans onto a train car stopped at a depot near Crescent View Farm. One man on left wears a uniform resembling that of a railroad conductor. Note: this image appears on two separate negatives.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Laborers; Cans; Carts & wagons; Railroad trains; Railroad employees
